sentence: how much does a first class round trip ticket from detroit to saint petersburg cost
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.fare_basis_code||'"', '"'||v1.class_type||'"',
 v0.round_trip_cost, '"'||v2.fare_id||'"', '"'||v3.flight_id||'"',
 '"'||v4.airport_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v5.city_name||'"', '"'||v6.airport_code||'"', '"'||v7.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.city_name||'"' FROM fare v0,
 fare_basis v1, flight_fare v2, flight v3, airport_service v4,
 city v5, airport_service v6, city v7 
WHERE (((v0.fare_basis_code = ANY v1.fare_basis_code) 
AND (v1.class_type = 'FIRST')) 
AND ((v0.round_trip_cost IS NOT NULL) AND ((v0.fare_id = ANY v2.fare_id) 
AND ((v2.flight_id = ANY v3.flight_id) AND (((v3.from_airport = ANY v4.airport_code) 
AND ((v4.city_code = ANY v5.city_code) 
AND (v5.city_name = 'DETROIT'))) AND ((v3.to_airport = ANY v6.airport_code) 
AND ((v6.city_code = ANY v7.city_code) 
AND (v7.city_name = 'ST. PETERSBURG'))))))));
